    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a superlative E92 M3, a final-act masterpiece featuring the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power unit, equipped with individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, delivers an unparalleled linear power band. Mated to a traditional 6-speed manual gearbox, the drivetrain offers pure mechanical engagement. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring long-term reliability. The chassis remains taut, featuring Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a variable M-differential lock for precision cornering. The exterior finish is flawless, free of rock chips or swirl marks, while the interior retains its factory-fresh matte finish on the Novillo leather. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example for the discerning enthusiast.",
