      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, boasting a mirror-like exterior finish with absolutely zero imperfections, stone chips, or swirl marks. The interior remains in a time-capsule state, featuring supple, untouched leather, pristine carpeting, and all original factory scent. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete, organized binder of maintenance records included. Mechanically, it operates with the silent precision and tight handling of a brand-new machine. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning enthusiast to acquire a flawless, collector-grade example that has never seen rain or snow.",
      "price": 48500.0,
